As a user(customer) 
I want to be able to sort items
So that I can faster find the necessary item

Scope

The sorting functionality
The item card
It should work in Chrome, Mozilla, Safari browsers
It should also work in Mobile


Precondition:

The sorting functionality is implemented


Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1: User can successfully sort items by: Recommended, Newest, Price (low to high), Price (high to low), Name A-Z, Name Z-A
Given: User on the "Shop" page
When: Select necessary type of sorting 
Then: The items are sorted











